headline: Is There Still Room for Growth in J&J Shares After Recent FDA Approval?
summary: Trying to figure out whether to hold, buy, or trim your Johnson & Johnson position? You are definitely not alone. This blue chip stock has a long history of resilience, but recent price movements have caused both excitement and caution among investors. Over just the past week, shares have climbed 2.0%, building on steady gains that have pushed the stock up 1.4% over the last month.
